 CAPTION;MDY;M;D;Y;LATD;LATM;NS;LONGD;LONGM;EW;DN;H;AP;LINE
‚ćĚ Prints header line matching book example:
‚ćĚ VIEW FROM {lat} NORTH, {long} WEST, ON {day} {date} AT {time}
‚ćĚ Uses globals: LAT, LONG, STATEDDAYNO, STATEDTIME
 MDY‚ÜźJNUINV STATEDDAYNO
 M‚ÜźMDY[1] ‚čĄ D‚ÜźMDY[2] ‚čĄ Y‚ÜźMDY[3]
 DN‚ÜźDAYNAME STATEDDAYNO
 ‚ćĚ Latitude: degrees and arcminutes
 LATD‚Üź‚Ćä|LAT
 LATM‚Üź‚Ćä0.5+60√ó(|LAT)-LATD
 NS‚Üź(1+LAT<0)‚äÉ'NORTH' 'SOUTH'
 ‚ćĚ Longitude: degrees and arcminutes
 LONGD‚Üź‚Ćä|LONG
 LONGM‚Üź‚Ćä0.5+60√ó(|LONG)-LONGD
 EW‚Üź(1+LONG>0)‚äÉ'WEST' 'EAST'
 ‚ćĚ Time: hours ‚Üí 12-hour with AM/PM
 H‚Üź12|STATEDTIME
 :If H=0 ‚čĄ H‚Üź12 ‚čĄ :EndIf
 AP‚Üź(1+STATEDTIME<12)‚äÉ'PM' 'AM'
 ‚ćĚ Assemble
 LINE‚Üź'VIEW FROM ',(‚ćēLATD),' DEGREES ',(‚ćēLATM),' MINUTES ',NS
 LINE‚ÜźLINE,', ',(‚ćēLONGD),' DEGREES ',(‚ćēLONGM),' MINUTES ',EW
